item.title: CVE-2021-38319|2024-08-04T01:37:16.388Z -- more%20from%20google -- more%20from%20google
item.description: The More From Google WordPress plugin is vulnerable to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting due to a reflected $_SERVER["PHP_SELF"] value in the ~/morefromgoogle.php file which allows attackers to inject arbitrary web scripts, in versions up to and including 0.0.2.
